data.description: Opportunities such as this are hard to come by.  This home starts with great curb appeal and then you'll step into vaulted ceilings, an open floor plan and a touch of vintage.  This home offers an ideal blend of style and comfort and amazing livability.  There are a lot of updates to brag about including some new windows, roof/gutters, landscaping, carpeting, a freshly painted exterior and interior, new gates, new fixtures and so much more.  The floor to ceiling windows bring in lots of light!  The kitchen comes fully equipped with all appliances including a new gas range, new disposal, and a new dishwasher.  Even the washer/dryer stays.  Enjoy the beautiful backyard oasis, perfect for relaxation and entertaining which flows perfectly from the all seasons room in back.  All this home needs is you and your personal touch.  Located in a prime, and central location, with amenities galore, plus in the Lindbergh School District. Lots of storage!  This one won't last long.  Come take a look!
